Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 客倌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出…出…出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山贼 杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近来尽出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无…无面鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无面鬼  那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉 那是我的木遁分身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长 太假戏真做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 鸣人还真胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长的脸是最有害心脏健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么挖苦我嘛 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这浓雾中 也没其他啥能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有大人像你这么说鬼故事的 感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为你胆小如鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不觉得那故事令人恐怖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就说个珍藏的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说每到这种时候就会出现那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:02:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了引导死者的灵魂 乌鸦作为先导出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帆柱上点亮的巨大鬼火就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓浓的大雾正是死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦相遇便会踏上前往死者国度的航程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是幽灵船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说就是这样的浓雾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 就是在这样的浓雾中现身的幽灵船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵船什么的不过是古老的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛 怎么可能有那种东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来我一点都没信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可没看出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有风吹动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵船…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的 要去幽灵船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 世上没有幽灵船什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是有吗 就在那里 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大和队长说的如出一辙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是艘很可疑的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据航海法 不可以对漂流船只置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧完成调查就能回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知如此 不如陪着浓眉老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 要坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要够坚强 管它是幽灵还是别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是先坚强点把晕船挺过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 青叶大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脸可不是地板 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个忙碌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用它来开船的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 这刷子真是历史悠久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是船长的贵重物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你明明是个小孩 却相当能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人比一个人强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过比起两人来 干活可是人越多越快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不赶紧搞定你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不太会停下跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 我叫飞石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人是忍者吗 很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目标直指火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里最强大最伟大的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那船长比火影更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长不仅要强大要伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要处处温柔地为伙伴着想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日 我也要成为一名船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 等…等等先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影不仅强大 伟大 温柔 为同伴着想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还相当有气度 那个…之后还有…之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是火影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩都有各自的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 教教我那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是之前用刷子锵锵敲地的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是船长教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把刷子也是船长送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否也让我们加入你们的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处搜查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不过是艘普通的船只 大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是幽灵船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么幽灵船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是迷信来着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个不是人的灵魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帆柱上的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在船员之间被称为幸运的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是发光的静电气而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静…静电气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么帆柱上的乌鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般情况下 乌鸦可不会出现在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半路休息的海鸟 被烟囱的烟给熏黑了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么幽灵船的话题就暂且告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们调查了一下这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船上除你之外 没有其他船员了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的船员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种级别的船 需要相当的人数来运作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 刷子船长也没在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴们曾经都在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起海里会有幽灵船这种愚蠢的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还潜藏着更恐怖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是传说的海怪 牟黑大螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 不仅仅是只螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同一座小岛般的巨型螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外壳坚硬无比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被那巨大的钳子抓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么都会被碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且寄生于外壳之上的富士壶专吃活人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长和其他人 大家…大家被那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 忍者很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒那家伙 替我给船长他们报仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 飞石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来打飞那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶大叔 带飞石回船里去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便替我转告大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解救大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止牟黑大螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有将这件事转告给同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事需要两个人来做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶大叔更能冷静地传达消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得相当可靠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 那个任务就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和那种怪物交战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧 我的目标可是当上火影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了伙伴 一点都不害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 你还小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有你一个得救也行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕 船长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从登上这艘船起 这东西就一直伴随我左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我保管好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了不少毛的刷子正是我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能替我保管好 我也就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有未完成的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了信任我跟随而来的同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要守护这艘船到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 我这就收拾掉你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是拯救了木叶村的英雄 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去我们的船上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋 竟敢威胁我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是个怪物 你这家伙才没啥可怕的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是怪物螃蟹 外壳太坚硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不仅坚硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还出人意料地敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶 我和船都摇晃不已 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧逃离这片海域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人正在为我们争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长 请给我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法用我的拿手本领一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶紧解救出大和队长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 请借我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关上了 飞石做到了吗 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然轻而易举被抓 真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和队长 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的外壳坚不可摧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说要瞄准柔软的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木遁之术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 把你的勇气借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧 怪物螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了飞石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你比我先实现愿望了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然时间短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经成为不输火影的伟大船长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时没能跟大家一同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在鸣人替我为大家报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉舒坦了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别抬举我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了飞石 才能打倒怪物螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你已经成为我们的同伴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过该告别了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 没人会责怪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这强烈的责任感还真让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你不能成佛 所以我们都无法成佛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 没什么好道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是被那混蛋螃蟹夺去了身躯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是相当舒坦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 就是 就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 借着气氛 大家来做例行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞石 多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,船舵不起作用了 这暴风雨真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去被卷到旋涡里怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能返回原定路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一口气直奔雷之国去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 鸣人 有什么东西过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传 战舰之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,炮击 哦 那是什么啊
